<p>Of course membership in WSFS is voluntary. Nobody is twisting your arm to join it. Naturally, if you don&#8217;t join, you can&#8217;t vote in the organization&#8217;s elections, any more than you could vote in your local Elks lodge elections if you weren&#8217;t a member, or something like that.</p>
