<p>In a country (the US) where less than fifty percent eligible vote in a presidential election, to have a percentage vote like this should tell the Hugo&#8217;s that even if they don&#8217;t like it, something is out of kilter.  That many people stood up and said something.</p>
<p>Perhaps, just perhaps, possibly, maybe&#8230;.that might be something to consider.</p>
