				<div class="comment-body"><p>William: The Hugo Awards are for Science Fiction <em>and Fantasy</em>; it&#8217;s in the official definition. They are no longer even officially the &#8220;Science Fiction Achievement Awards.&#8221; The official name of the Hugo Award is &#8220;Hugo Award.&#8221; That&#8217;s how the <em>Harry Potter</em> work was eligible.</p>
</div>

