<p>&#8220;No Award&#8221; is to be used if you honestly believe that no author on the nominee list is &#8220;worthy&#8221; and/or &#8220;deserving&#8221; of the award. Which you have already said you feel sorry for a couple of the authors which means that you do feel they should have some chance at the award.</p>
