		<div id="comment-371306">
			<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/aef52c634a08457275107f4756c94bb8?s=40&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/aef52c634a08457275107f4756c94bb8?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' />				<cite class="fn">janmaus</cite> <span class="says">says:</span>			</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
				
